ynergism', 'The risk of hepatic injury should be considered when brentuximab vedotin is used with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/296930/', '', 'Paritaprevir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Valaciclovir, Dolutegravir, Oseltamivir, Acyclovir, Brincidofovir, Elbasvir, Famciclovir, Doravirine, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
